Francais,Moore,Verset
,A Zakoob le sɩnga kẽnd n tees yaang sẽnẽ.,1
,"A waa n yãee bulga, la bulga sɛɛga a yãee dũms bõones bãg a tã; rũmsa ra paamda koom be n yũuda; kugr ninga sẽn tar n pagd bulga noorã yaool n da yaa kug bedre.",2
,Yaa rũmsa sẽn wat n tigim taaba la b lakd kugrã n yũnug-ba n le lebs-a n page.,3
,A Zakoob soka rũm-kɩɩmbã: «Yãmb yita yɛ?» Tɩ b yeele: «Tõnd yita Aram.»,4
,T'a sok-ba «Yãmb mi-la a Nawor biig a Labã bɩ?» Tɩ b yet tɩ: «N-yẽe!»,5
,T'a sok-ba: «A bee laafi?» Tɩ b yeele: «Laafi be! La ad-a biig a Rasɛl sẽn wat ne rũmsi.»,6
,T'a Zakoob yeele: «Wĩndig ketame la rũmsa kõom nan pa ta ye. Yũnug-y-ba la y leb n wãben-ba.»,7
,"Dẽ la b leok-a: «B ka tõe n yũ nand ye, rẽnd b fãa tigim taaba tɩ b yaool n lak kugrã n paam n kõ-b tɩ b yũ.»",8
,"A Zakoob ra ket n sõsda ne rũm-kɩɩmbã, la a Rasɛl taa bulgã ne a ba wã rũmsi; yẽ n da gũud rũmsã.",9
,"A Zakoob sẽn yãee a Rasɛl, a yɛsb a Labã biiga, a sẽn yãe rũmsã, a kolgame n lak kugrã n kõ-b koom.",10
,"A Zakoob mobga a Rasɛl, n lɛɛg n sɩng yãbre.",11
,"A wilga a Rasɛl t'a ba wã ne yẽ yaa rogem, t'a yaa a Rebeka biiga la a Rasɛl wudg n tɩ togsa a ba.",12
,"A Labã me sẽn wʋm t'a Zakoob yaa a tão biiga, a zoe n tɩ seg-a lame, tɩ b pʋʋs taab wa neb sẽn nong taaba la b rɩk yir sore. A da kelgda a Zakoob sẽn da kõt-a kibɛ niynsã.",13
,A Labã yeelame: «F yĩng yi-la m yĩngẽ la f kõbr yi-la m kõabẽ.» A Zakoob paa ne-a kiuug tõre.,14
,,
,"A Labã yeela a Zakoob: «Tõnd yaa buudu, la ka rẽ yĩng la f na n tʋm m zaka tʋʋma n ka reeg yaood ye; wilg maam f yaood sẽn tog n yɩ a soaba.»",15
,"A Labã kom-pugli wã ra ya-la b yiibu: a Lea, kãsma, a Rasɛl, yao wã.",16
,A Lea nina ra yaa nin-bʋgsg soab nini; a Rasɛl yagd da pida zãnga t'a neng ya neere.,17
,"A Zakoob sẽn da nong a soaba yaa a Rasɛl; dẽ la a yeel a Labã: «M na n tʋma f zakẽ yʋʋm a yopoe, tɩ f kõ maam yao wã, a Rasɛl.»",18
,"T'a Labã na n yeele: «M menga neeme tɩ m sã n dɩk-a n kõ foo n são m sã n dɩk-a n kõ sãana, woto wã pa ne maam.»",19
,,
,"A Zakoob tʋma yʋʋm a yopoe, a Rasɛl daab yĩnga. La a sẽn da nong-a wʋsga yĩnga, yʋʋm a yopoe wã yɩ wa rasem a yopoe.",20
,A Zakoob waa n yeela a Labã: «M tẽed tɩ wakata taame la m datame t'a Rasɛl lebg m paga.»,21
,A Labã tigsa tẽnga neba fãa n segl dɩɩb n kõ-ba.,22
,"Zĩig sẽn sobge, a rɩka a Lea n kõ a Zakoob t'a kẽ ne-a.",23
,A Labã rɩka a Zilpa n kõ a Lea t'a maan a roog-biiga.,24
,"Zĩig sẽn yẽege, a Zakoob yãeeme tɩ yaa a Lea la a paam yã, t'a yeel a Labã: «Kato! Yaa bõe la f maan-ma, ka a Rasɛl yĩng la m da tʋmd la? Bõe yĩng tɩ f maan-m zãmbo?»",25
,T'a Labã na n leoke: «Ad tõnd zamaanẽ wã yẽer pa rengd a kẽem n kul sɩd ye.,26
,"Vʋʋs ne tʋʋma rasem a yopoe, f kãadma ne a Lea yĩnga. Dẽ poore, m na rɩk a Rasɛl n paas-fo la fo na le tʋm m yĩnga, yʋʋm a yopoe yɛsa.»",27
,"A Zakoob maana boto, a rɩ-la a yikãadma kibs rasem a yopoe, dẽ poore a Labã rɩka a Rasɛl n paas-a.",28
,A Labã rɩka a Bila n kõ a Rasɛl t'a maan a roog biiga.,29
,"A Zakoob kẽe ne a Rasɛl. A ra nonga yẽ n yɩɩd a Lea. A Zakoob paasa yʋʋm a yopoe, a yɛsba yiri.",30
,,
,"Soaala yãeeme t'a Zakoob pa get a Lea yell neer ye, tɩ b yeel tɩ yẽnda la b na n kõ kamba n yaool n mong a Rasɛl.",31
,A Lea rɩka pʋga n dog a biiga n pʋda yʋʋr a Rubẽ; la rẽ yaa a sẽn da yeel a sũurẽ: «Soaala-Wẽnd yãenda m nimbãanega la rũnda tɛka m sɩda na nong-m n yɩɩd pĩnda.»,32
,A Lea sẽn le rɩk pʋga a dogame n pʋd bi-kãng t'a Simeõ: tɩ biig la a le paam yɛsa n kõ a sɩda la raare nonglma na paase.,33
,"A Lea le rɩka pʋga n dog biiga la a yeelame tɩ marsã wã yẽ, nonglem na zĩndi tɩ yaa kamb a tãab la a kõ a sɩda. Biiga pʋdame tɩ Levi.",34
,"A Lea le rɩka pʋg n le rog biiga n yetẽ: «Marsã m na pẽg Soaala-Wẽnd.» Rẽ la a pʋd a biiga Zɩɩda, la a pa le paam dogem ye.",35
